metadata.description: AI FOUND OBJECT ANIMAL ART: BABY's FIRST NFTs. A super cute AI-created collection of animal toys made from found objects. A unique greeting for any baby's first NFT. Each mint includes one of these many possible animal toys:  ANT, BEAR, BIRD, CAMEL, CAT, CATERPILLAR, DOG, DUCK, ELEPHANT, FISH, FOX, GIRAFFE, HORSE, IGUANA, JAGUAR, KANGAROO, KITTEN, LION, MONKEY, MOUSE, NARWAL, OSTRICH, PEACOCK, PIGLET, PUPPY, QUAIL, RABBIT, RACCOON, ROOSTER, SCORPION, SKUNK, SNAKE, TIGER, TURTLE, UNICORN, VULTURE, WOLF, YAK, YELLOW JACKET, ZEBRA. Which one will you or your recipient receive?
